{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb6078530-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"299c–4"},"text":"§ 299c–4.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional provisions with respect to grants and contracts","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6078531-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Financial conflicts of interest","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"With respect to projects for which awards of grants, cooperative agreements, or contracts are authorized to be made under this subchapter, the Director shall by regulation define—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6078532-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the specific circumstances that constitute financial interests in such projects that will, or may be reasonably expected to, create a bias in favor of obtaining results in the projects that are consistent with such interests; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6078533-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the actions that will be taken by the Director in response to any such interests identified by the Director.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6078534-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Requirement of application","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Director may not, with respect to any program under this subchapter authorizing the provision of grants, cooperative agreements, or contracts, provide any such financial assistance unless an application for the assistance is submitted to the Secretary and the application is in such form, is made in such manner, and contains such agreements, assurances, and information as the Director determines to be necessary to carry out the program involved.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6078535-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Provision of supplies and services in lieu of funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6078536-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Upon the request of an entity receiving a grant, cooperative agreement, or contract under this subchapter, the Secretary may, subject to paragraph (2), provide supplies, equipment, and services for the purpose of aiding the entity in carrying out the project involved and, for such purpose, may detail to the entity any officer or employee of the Department of Health and Human Services.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb6078537-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Corresponding reduction in funds","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"With respect to a request described in paragraph (1), the Secretary shall reduce the amount of the financial assistance involved by an amount equal to the costs of detailing personnel and the fair market value of any supplies, equipment, or services provided by the Director. The Secretary shall, for the payment of expenses incurred in complying with such request, expend the amounts withheld.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb6078538-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s299c–4/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Applicability of certain provisions with respect to contracts","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Contracts may be entered into under this part without regard to section 3324(a) and (b) of title 31 and ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s6101"},"text":"section 6101 of title 41","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb6078539-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373"},"text":"July 1, 1944, ch. 373","children":[],"tail":", title IX, § 945, formerly § 925, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/129/s2/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–129, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-12-06"},"text":"Dec. 6, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/1668"},"text":"113 Stat. 1668","